etshuffle.com/index.php/1987/02/11/cover-me-down-the-road-apiece/", "url_meta": {"origin": 29626, "position": 1}, "title": "Down the Road Apiece", "author": "Ken", "date": "February 11, 1987", "format": false, "excerpt": "From Bruce's pre-E Street Days to just pre-pandemic, \"Down the Road Apiece\" has always been an epic, crowd-pleasing jam. Let's watch and listen to some of the best inside.", "rel": "", "context": "In &quot;Cover Me&quot;", "block_context": {"text": "Cover Me", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/category/cover-me/"}, "img": {"alt_text": "", "src": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/PIECECOVER_1024x1024%402x.jpg?fit=1199%2C1200&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200", "width": 350, "height": 200, "srcset": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/PIECECOVER_1024x1024%402x.jpg?fit=1199%2C1200&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200 1x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/PIECECOVER_1024x1024%402x.jpg?fit=1199%2C1200&ssl=1&resize=525%2C300 1.5x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/PIECECOVER_1024x1024%402x.jpg?fit=1199%2C1200&ssl=1&resize=700%2C400 2x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/PIECECOVER_1024x1024%402x.jpg?fit=1199%2C1200&ssl=1&resize=1050%2C600 3x"}, "classes": []}, {"id": 57109, "url": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2025/06/18/kingdom-of-days-june-18-2/", "url_meta": {"origin": 29626, "position": 2}, "title": "June 18", "author": "Ken", "date": "June 18, 2025", "format": false, "excerpt": "Rest in peace, Clarence \"Big Man\" Clemons. Clarence passed away on this date in 2011, but watch his magical performance with Bruce--just the two of them--from this date in 1988.", "rel": "", "context": "In &quot;Kingdom of Days&quot;", "block_context": {"text": "Kingdom of Days", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/category/kingdom-of-days/"}, "img": {"alt_text": "", "src": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/bigman.jpg?fit=1200%2C800&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200", "width": 350, "height": 200, "srcset": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/bigman.jpg?fit=1200%2C800&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200 1x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/bigman.jpg?fit=1200%2C800&ssl=1&resize=525%2C300 1.5x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/bigman.jpg?fit=1200%2C800&ssl=1&resize=700%2C400 2x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/bigman.jpg?fit=1200%2C800&ssl=1&resize=1050%2C600 3x"}, "classes": []}, {"id": 59655, "url": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2025/09/14/kingdom-of-days-september-14-2/", "url_meta": {"origin": 29626, "position": 3}, "title": "September 14", "author": "Ken", "date": "September 14, 2025", "format": false, "excerpt": "Both River tours ended on this date; check out highlights from each inside, plus: Ed Norton interviews Bruce on stage in Toronto, and on the Rising Tour, Bruce starts rediscovering his missing years.", "rel": "", "context": "In &quot;Kingdom of Days&quot;", "block_context": {"text": "Kingdom of Days", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/category/kingdom-of-days/"}, "img": {"alt_text": "", "src": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/admin-ajax-90.jpg?fit=1200%2C1200&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200", "width": 350, "height": 200, "srcset": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/admin-ajax-90.jpg?fit=1200%2C1200&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200 1x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/admin-ajax-90.jpg?fit=1200%2C1200&ssl=1&resize=525%2C300 1.5x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/admin-ajax-90.jpg?fit=1200%2C1200&ssl=1&resize=700%2C400 2x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/admin-ajax-90.jpg?fit=1200%2C1200&ssl=1&resize=1050%2C600 3x"}, "classes": []}, {"id": 58369, "url": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2025/08/12/kingdom-of-days-august-12-2/", "url_meta": {"origin": 29626, "position": 4}, "title": "August 12", "author": "Ken", "date": "August 12, 2025", "format": false, "excerpt": "On this date: Mitch Ryder makes a \"Detroit Medley\" guest appearance, Bruce swings by the Yankees' clubhouse, the debut of the acoustic \"Countin' on a Miracle\" video, and more.", "rel": "", "context": "In &quot;Kingdom of Days&quot;", "block_context": {"text": "Kingdom of Days", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/category/kingdom-of-days/"}, "img": {"alt_text": "", "src": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/19990812_2_front.jpg?fit=1076%2C928&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200", "width": 350, "height": 200, "srcset": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/19990812_2_front.jpg?fit=1076%2C928&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200 1x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/19990812_2_front.jpg?fit=1076%2C928&ssl=1&resize=525%2C300 1.5x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/19990812_2_front.jpg?fit=1076%2C928&ssl=1&resize=700%2C400 2x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/19990812_2_front.jpg?fit=1076%2C928&ssl=1&resize=1050%2C600 3x"}, "classes": []}, {"id": 57513, "url": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2025/06/27/kingdom-of-days-june-27-2/", "url_meta": {"origin": 29626, "position": 5}, "title": "June 27", "author": "Ken", "date": "June 27, 2025", "format": false, "excerpt": "For a rare song, \"Janey, Don't You Lose Heart\" is performed on two different occasions on this date. Plus: a complete 1982 bar gig, Bruce headlines Glastonbury, and more.", "rel": "", "context": "In &quot;Kingdom of Days&quot;", "block_context": {"text": "Kingdom of Days", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/category/kingdom-of-days/"}, "img": {"alt_text": "", "src": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/BS_LOST_BOX_cover_2000x2056.webp?fit=1168%2C120